                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker. I produce some sheets and a table cloth pawned by the prisoner, it the name of Elizabeth Coles, by James Jennings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Are you quite sure he is the man? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes; I do not know who Elizabeth Coles is—he us to understand she was his mistress.</p>
